    public abstract class Model_Drone
extends Model
    This class represents all airborne models. It uses standard flight dynamics parameters yaw, pitch, roll, and gaz, and provides methods predict(), updatePos(), inMotion(), collision(), and updateSensor() used in other classes. Subclasses must override the abstract methods, making sure each returns a constant value.
